BT 1 0 0 1 0 86 Tm /F4 10 Tf 16 TL .8985 Tw (The controller of the entire system. It connects every class together. It handles all Scanner input and all screen output. It) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.661 Tw (shows the login screen, routes to admin or staff menu based on who is logged in, handles every menu choice in) Tj T* 0 Tw .815 Tw (handleInput\(\), and calls the correct class method for each action. On startup it loads data and runs alerts. On shutdown it) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.134 Tw (saves inventory and creates a backup. When the GUI module is taught, only this class needs to be replaced with Swing) Tj T* 0 Tw .69 Tw (windows \227 every other class stays exactly as it is because the business logic was kept completely separate from the user) Tj T* 0 Tw (interface.) Tj T* ET
